Program: Discovery
Title: The Future of the Forests
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxnj
Last Broadcast Date: 24 July 2000
Report on the deforestation occurring in developing nations of the tropical world. Over 14 million hectares of forest are lost annually. For developing nations the forests may be one of the largest resource they have. Can developing nations continue to develop without deforestation; the programme looks at alternatives to and possible solutions. Show less